@baseUrl = https://localhost:7113
@token = YOUR_JWT_HERE

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "Customer123!",
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

### Login (admin seed: admin@ecommerce.local / Admin123!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ecommerce.local",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Products (paged, anonymous)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/Products?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=price&sortDescending=true

### Create product (Admin + Bearer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/Products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "USB-C Cable",
  "description": "1m braided",
  "price": 12.99,
  "stockQuantity": 200,
  "sku": "USB-C-1M",
  "categoryIds": []
}

### Checkout (User + Bearer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/Orders/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
